# django-twilio-call

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-twilio-call.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-twilio-call)
[![Python Support](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/django-twilio-call.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/django-twilio-call/)
[![Django Support](https://img.shields.io/badge/django-4.2%20%7C%205.0%20%7C%205.1-44B78B)](https://www.djangoproject.com/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Tests](https://github.com/hmesfin/django-twilio-call/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/hmesfin/django-twilio-call/actions)
[![Coverage](https://codecov.io/gh/hmesfin/django-twilio-call/branch/main/graph/badge.svg)](https://codecov.io/gh/hmesfin/django-twilio-call)
[![Documentation](https://readthedocs.org/projects/django-twilio-call/badge/?version=latest)](https://django-twilio-call.readthedocs.io/)

**django-twilio-call** is an enterprise-grade Django package for building sophisticated call center applications using Twilio's powerful communication APIs. Build production-ready call centers with features like IVR, call routing, recording, real-time monitoring, and comprehensive analytics.

## âœ¨ Features

### Core Call Center Functionality
- ğŸ“ **Inbound/Outbound Calls** - Handle both incoming and outgoing calls with ease
- ğŸ”€ **Intelligent Call Routing** - Route calls based on skills, availability, and priority
- ğŸ‘¥ **Agent Management** - Complete agent system with status tracking and queue assignment
- ğŸ“Š **Queue Management** - Sophisticated queue system with priority and overflow handling
- ğŸ™ï¸ **Call Recording** - Record calls with compliance features and transcription support
- ğŸ”Š **IVR System** - Build complex Interactive Voice Response flows
- ğŸ¯ **Real-time Monitoring** - Track call center metrics and agent performance in real-time

### Enterprise Features
- ğŸ” **JWT Authentication** - Secure API access with JSON Web Tokens
- âš¡ **Rate Limiting** - Protect your APIs from abuse with configurable rate limits
- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **RBAC** - Role-Based Access Control for agents and supervisors
- ğŸ“ˆ **Analytics & Reporting** - Comprehensive call analytics and performance metrics
- ğŸ”„ **WebSocket Support** - Real-time updates for live dashboards
- ğŸ“¡ **Webhook Handling** - Secure webhook processing with signature validation
- âš™ï¸ **Celery Integration** - Asynchronous task processing for scalability

### Production Ready
- ğŸ³ **Docker Support** - Complete Docker configuration for easy deployment
- â˜¸ï¸ **Kubernetes Ready** - Kubernetes manifests for cloud-native deployment
- ğŸ“Š **Monitoring** - Prometheus metrics and health check endpoints
